FBIS3-18305 "drweu040_i_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 FRANCE Mitterrand Condemns `Abominable Hebron Massacre' LD2802205594 Paris France-2 Television Network in French 1900 GMT 28 Feb 94 LD2802205594 Paris France-2 Television Network Language: French Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] President Mitterrand sent messages to Yitzhaq Rabin and Yasir 'Arafat this weekend. The head of state condemned, I quote, the abominable Hebron massacre. The French president concluded by saying: Progress toward peace is more urgent than ever. [passage omitted]
